      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="law">
      <h2>Governing law and disputes</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, United States, without regard to its conflict-of-laws rules. You and rekody agree to bring any dispute exclusively in the state or federal courts located in California, and both parties consent to personal jurisdiction there.
      </p>
