      </p>
      <p>
        If you're a consumer in the EU, UK, or another jurisdiction where mandatory local law gives you broader rights than the above, that local law applies to the extent it cannot be waived.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="changes">
      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. If we make material changes, we'll update the "Last updated" date at the top and notify active subscribers by email at least 30 days before the change takes effect. Continuing to use the service after the effective date means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>
      <p>
        Historical versions are available on request.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Support, billing, legal, and privacy: <a href="mailto:support@rekody.com">support@rekody.com</a><br/>
        Security disclosures: <a href="mailto:security@rekody.com">security@rekody.com</a><br/>
        Press and general inquiries: <a href="mailto:hi@rekody.com">hi@rekody.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        rekody is operated by Tony Kipkemboi (d/b/a rekody), United States. Full mailing address available on request.
      </p>
    </section>
  </LegalPage>
</Base>
